  .verses.mt-4
    +verse('Mark 16:15-16'): | And He said to them, #[q.jesus Go into all the world and preach the gospel to every creature. He who believes and is baptized will be saved; but he who does not believe will be condemned.]
    +verse('Mat.10:7-8'): q.jesus And as you go, preach, saying, 'The kingdom of heaven is at hand.' Heal the sick, cleanse the lepers, raise the dead, cast out demons. Freely you have received, freely give.
  p: :link To help with this endeavour, I have created these gospel tracts. You can find the PDFs and [source code here](https://github.com/christ-resurrected/gospel-tracts).
